.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, lime, onion
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, traveling
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, chinese, spanish
City: venice, liverpool, colone
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, swimming
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 3. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the chinese##1
 6. the australian is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating apple##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating apple is on the right of the fan of folk##1
10. the chinese is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is the spanish##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
14. the chinese is in an odd position##4
15. the person traveling to venice is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food          | lime     | apple      | onion      |
| Hobby         | chess    | traveling  | card-games |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | juice   | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | hip-hop    | disco      |
| Nationality   | spanish  | australian | chinese    |
| City           | liverpool    | venice       | colone     |
| Sport         | parkour  | baseball   | swimming   |

