 4. the dressmaker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is the journalist##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who likes light-blue is between the person eating pineapple and the dressmaker##2
10. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person driving the scooter is the person driving the scooter##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
13. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the scooter##1
